{"tid":768032,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港從來都唔係一個睇實力既地方","createTime":"2018-08-05T05:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T07:46:28.000Z","uid":198289,"like":11,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6a60fce85249dbbc96ff8f3f8b2501ed9fa08d","tid":768032,"uid":198289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:10:12.000Z","msg":"睇完全民造星真係好嬲<br />\n要抒發下自己<br />\n點解一個電視台唔可以正正經經做個音樂節目出黎<br />\n因為你班香港人唔鐘意睇呀嘛<br />\n香港人永遠都鐘意笑9人 多過欣賞人<br />\n呢樣野台灣日本真係做得好太多<br />\n某某某係香港出新歌 下面留言永遠都係多數踩<br />\n咁到底係班香港人唔夠實力比香港人欣賞<br />\n定根本香港人天性係鐘意踩人？"},{"pid":"dfc39a9e51d1f008940772af4e734fa6c3032a80","tid":768032,"uid":198289,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3d6a60fce85249dbbc96ff8f3f8b2501ed9fa08d","tid":768032,"uid":198289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:10:12.000Z","msg":"睇完全民造星真係好嬲<br />\n要抒發下自己<br />\n點解一個電視台唔可以正正經經做個音樂節目出黎<br />\n因為你班香港人唔鐘意睇呀嘛<br />\n香港人永遠都鐘意笑9人 多過欣賞人<br />\n呢樣野台灣日本真係做得好太多<br />\n某某某係香港出新歌 下面留言永遠都係多數踩<br />\n咁到底係班香港人唔夠實力比香港人欣賞<br />\n定根本香港人天性係鐘意踩人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:12:52.000Z","msg":"入圍55個 何來潛質與實力<br />\n造星睇外表我明呀<br />\n但真係高大哂？<br />\n高得黎唔洗睇樣？<br />\n個樣唔夠好可以化妝<br />\n身高唔夠著對高靴加下鞋墊<br />\n但係音癡到底可以點救？"},{"pid":"27bdafee25035a8727a3fbe33622cafdd472f239","tid":768032,"uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:12:59.000Z","msg":"My name is Frank. That's not important. The important question is: who are you? America has become a cruel and vicious place. We reward the shallowest, the dumbest, the meanest and the loudest. We no longer have any common sense of decency. No sense of shame. There is no right and wrong. The worst qualities in people are looked up to and celebrated. Lying and spreading fear is fine as long as you make money doing it. We've become a nation of slogan-saying, bile-spewing hatemongers. We've lost our kindness. We've lost our soul. What have we become? We take the weakest in our society, we hold them up 